2024-05-10T00:05:00.000Z | prod-delta      | 0.1733333
2024-05-10T00:05:00.000Z | prod-null       | 0.2766667
2024-05-10T00:10:00.000Z | prod-cumulative | 0.2733333
2024-05-10T00:10:00.000Z | prod-delta      | 0.1766667
2024-05-10T00:10:00.000Z | prod-null       | 0.2733333
